{"id":306550,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-成都维权人士为被关押的许乃来六岁女儿/","date":"2013-07-31T06:18:37Z","modified":"2013-07-31T06:18:37Z","title":"维权网 | 成都维权人士为被关押的许乃来六岁女儿许严之捐款（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员陈华报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>，成都访民从维权网上得知维权人士许乃来到美国大使馆以献爱心的形式捐款，被北京市公安局朝阳分局当场抓走，其</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>岁的女儿许严之无人照顾，生活困顿的消息后，便自发的来到一起，为被刑拘的维权人士许乃来的六岁女儿捐款。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>很多访民因多年上访，经济拮据，自己生存都很艰难，但还是纷纷解囊，对小严之的遭遇深表同情并十分牵挂，强烈谴责当局置幼小生命于不顾的反人类行径，表示不管遭遇多大的打压，一人有难，都会大家一起担当。大家守望相助，为维护公民的权利而抗争。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>捐款的维权访民有：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>黄晓敏</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 50</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>陈云飞</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 50</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>王蓉文</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 50</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>李双德</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 10</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>周成群</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 20</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>彭天惠</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 20</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>彭明贵</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 20</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>吴俊梅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>刘辉涛</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 10</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>曾</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>远</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 10</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>李廷惠</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 10</span><span>元</span><span lang=\"EN-US